These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: brazilian, argentine, french, australian
1. Nationality:argentine is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:australian is between Nationality:brazilian and Nationality:argentine##2
3. Nationality:australian is on the right of Nationality:brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | brazilian | australian | argentine | french |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: raspberry, corn, apricot, mango
1. Food:raspberry is on the left of Food:mango##1
2. Food:corn is in an odd position##4
3. Food:corn is on the left or right of Food:raspberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | corn | raspberry | mango | apricot |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: action, sports, epic, fantasy
1. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:action##3
2. Movie-Genre:action is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:epic is between Movie-Genre:fantasy and Movie-Genre:sports##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | action | fantasy | epic | sports |

 #################################
 
