.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: banana, garlic, plum, zucchini
1. Food:garlic == Food:garlic##1
2. Food:zucchini is on the left or right of Food:plum##3
3. Food:plum is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:banana is in an even position##4
5. Food:zucchini is on the left of Food:garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | plum | zucchini | garlic | banana |

